headline: GTA Online
subtitle: North Yankton Nightmare Community Challenge
content:
You've already smashed the North Yankton Nightmare Community Challenge so the Orange Glow Skeleton Onesie and Red Hooded Skull Mask will be delivered in the coming days.

There's now a new goal of 800 million zombies. If the community is successful, we'll award all players the Purple Glow and Green Glow Skeleton Onesies.
